questions.quote: No, no, no Ross! Ross, these are friends of mine from home. Liam, Devon, this is Ross.
Okay, look, yesterday I would've even considered calling her back, but my ex-wife calls on the same day I have a near death experience. I mean, that-that has got to mean something!
And tell them that in 2 weeks I will once again be a masseuse in good standing!
Really? Oh What A Beautiful Morning! Surrey With A Fringe On Top.
Yeah, we were just talking about that. I can't believe how stupid we used to look.
That's way uptown! That's like three trains away! Which is great! I love to ride that rail!

yeah just some good old fashion girl on girl American action.
